  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Les Mélèzes is situated in the heart of Arc 2000and offers great views, as well as some fantastic spa facilities. With such close proximity to the slopes, only 70 metres away, the Hotel Mélèzes offers a convenient and comfortable stay for couples, friends and families looking to stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>.</p>
<h2><strong>Unbeatable location </strong></h2>
<p>Located in the centre of Les Arcs you have easy access to the 425km of slopes in the <a data-udi="umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b}" title="Paradiski Ski Area">Paradiski Area</a> which are just a short ski or walk away. Given its location, you have fantastic panoramic views of the surrounding mountains including Mont Blanc from the sunny south west facing terrace. Take in the scenic views at breakfast or in the evening, you can enjoy <span>sociable aperitif and watch the sunset over the snowy peaks.</span></p>
<h2><strong>Wellness facilities </strong></h2>
<p>Make the most of the <span>The Aquarelaxant area within the hotel after a day on the slopes. To avoid overcrowding adults have three free entries per week on a reservation only basis, so you can thoroughly relax in the spa. The wellness area has whirlpool baths, a sauna, a steam room and a hydro-massage shower to relieve your muscles after a day on the slopes. Treat yourself to a beauty treatment or massage at the in-house MMV Spa which can be booked for a local fee. </span><span></span></p>
<h2>Family friendly </h2>
<p><span>Hotel Mélèzes </span><span>is a great option for children looking to make new friends on your family ski holiday. There are a </span><span>number of children's clubs run by the hotel for children between 18 months to 17 years, providing all the fun from indoor games, snowball fights and virtual reality headsets. Be sure to register with the hotel on your arrival as spaces can be limited. </span></p>]]></description>
